NaviCharaList.name: Folon
NaviCharaList.description:
A seriously energetic fairy of time.
She is said to hold a great secret
in her watch.

NaviCharaList.name: Rena
NaviCharaList.description:
A fairy of time who loves history.
Many are afraid of what would happen
if her reading is interrupted..

NaviCharaList.name: Astrea
NaviCharaList.description:
A fairy of time who loves to fight.
She says to never miss a training
session in case of emergency.

NaviCharaList.name: Maya
NaviCharaList.description:
A carefree fairy of time.
Her mysterious bag is
apparently full of treasures.
